0.NAME: Title Match
0.EXPLANATION:
A fight to determine the best of the best. The winner of this will
hold the title belt for the Underground Coliseum! No excuses
allowed. This is a mano a mano, knock-down-drag-out fight!

1.NAME: Maximum Grand Prix
1.EXPLANATION:
Men who fight here aren't just strong, they are maximum
strength strong! Get ready for battles of maximum proportions
like you've never seen before! Witness the spirit of fighters who
have endured years of intense training to reach this ring!

2.NAME: Magnum Force Grand Prix
2.EXPLANATION:
A gathering of the strongest fighters and the finest fights!
Behold, as the curtain rises on the most extreme grand prix!
Which fighter will risk everything to win his way to the top?

3.NAME: Hyper Grand Prix
3.EXPLANATION:
The great fighting stage has just opened its doors! See
the evolution of no holds barred battles! Which fighter
will capture the wealth and fame of the fighting underground?

4.NAME: Twin Dragon Grand Prix
4.EXPLANATION:
A grand prix only for select tag fighting teams! These ultimate
team duos can unleash powerful and destructive attacks!
The top tag team of the Underground Coliseum will be decided
here!

5.NAME: Tag Match Grand Prix
5.EXPLANATION:
A new tag match grand prix! Tough veterans of the underground
fighting circuit will unite to battle together! Which team will
enjoy the sweet taste of victory?

6.NAME: Weapon Master Grand Prix
6.EXPLANATION:
A weapon based combat grand prix! Experience the impact of
well honed weapon techniques, never seen before in hand to
hand combat! The epitome of weapons combat has arrived!

7.NAME: Bomber Grand Prix
7.EXPLANATION:
Fight for your life in this grand prix of raining bombs! Evade
countless bombs or use them against your opponents in
your fight for victory! Who will emerge victorious from the
explosive blasts!?

8.NAME: Bounding Grand Prix
8.EXPLANATION:
A grand prix in a roped ring! The ring's sturdy ropes will
bounce back opponents who fly into them! Special
Underground Coliseum gloves also allow fighters to
send their opponents flying farther than normal!

9.NAME: Heat Grand Prix
9.EXPLANATION:
A grand prix set upon a heated iron plate! These fights will
burn up the fighters and fans alike with excitement! Don't
miss the hottest battles in the Underground Coliseum!

10.NAME: Breakout Grand Prix
10.EXPLANATION:
Falling out of this ring means immediate defeat! Don't let
the wire fence lull you into a false sense of security! Drop
your guard and you might get sent flying through the
fence! Which fighter will survive to the end?

11.NAME: Street Fight Grand Prix
11.EXPLANATION:
Deadly weapons and foul play welcome! A grand prix for street
fighters set in a complete reproduction of a Kamurocho street,
right here in the ring! Pick up weapons off the ground and
attack your opponents for the win!

12.NAME: Exhibition Tournament
12.EXPLANATION:
A gathering of Kamurocho fighters who think they've got what it
takes! A chance for rookie fighters to grab their first victory!
Don't miss a chance to see the next rising star!

13.EXPLANATION: You cannot participate in this grand prix yet.
